{"tid":2428182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"售貨員膠欄堵路阻警車行駛 今獲判感化18個月","createTime":"2021-03-01T11:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T12:53:43.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3007594dd0a04725d5e339b474243554d154b96b","tid":2428182,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"去年5月市民於銅鑼灣發起流水式遊行，反對訂立國安法，其後遭警方施放催淚彈驅散。其間一名年輕售貨員用膠欄堵路，早前承認一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，今被判接受感化18個月，另須支付訟費1,000元。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，當日下午約4時半，警員乘警車巡邏期間，發現被告將膠圍欄扔在菲林明道及軒尼詩道交界，阻礙一輛警車行駛，<span class=\"red\">過程被閉路電視拍下</span>。被告最後在灣仔A3出口外被截停，警誡及會面下均沒有說話。警方事後檢獲一把黃色雨傘及一個灰色腰包。"},{"pid":"d1697dd230e96d4442743b314164f81a5acd4dfa","tid":2428182,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/ESU5UQCVHJC3BJO47Q2MBOIIJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FESU5UQCVHJC3BJO47Q2MBOIIJY%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=c7447e5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FESU5UQCVHJC3BJO47Q2MBOIIJY%2F&h=f810a340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/ESU5UQCVHJC3BJO47Q2MBOIIJY/</a>"},{"pid":"d85b2e411bbf01b32f815ad0301cdbccce24fd1a","tid":2428182,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4c06d95cec263d01bbd4d0f994dc11a2526fb1","tid":2428182,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"走得就走。等睇班DoJ上訴"},{"pid":"8595d9033f6599f90e878733f4089264825d7138","tid":2428182,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:58: